10#include <stdio.h>
11#include <string.h>
12#include <openssl/ripemd.h>
13#include <openssl/crypto.h>
14
15unsigned char *RIPEMD160(const unsigned char *d, size_t n, unsigned char *md)
16{
17 RIPEMD160_CTX c;
18 static unsigned char m[RIPEMD160_DIGEST_LENGTH];
19
20 if (md == NULL)
21 md = m;
22 if (!RIPEMD160_Init(&c))
23 return NULL;
24 RIPEMD160_Update(&c, d, n);
25 RIPEMD160_Final(md, &c);
26 OPENSSL_cleanse(&c, sizeof(c)); /* security consideration */
27 return md;
28}
